data.description: Seller is willing to provide a SELLER CREDIT to replace the carpet or to install a fence. Introducing your dream home in the Cypress Creek community of Ruskin, FL! This stunning new listing boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a versatile loft and den. With a 2-car garage, this home offers both style and functionality. Situated in a serene setting, you'll enjoy the tranquility of having no backyard neighbors and a picturesque pond view. The open-concept living area is perfect for entertaining, and the modern kitchen features sleek appliances and ample counter space. The spacious master suite is your private oasis, complete with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom for relaxation. Three additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. Step outside to your own backyard paradise, where you can unwind on the patio and take in the breathtaking water views. This Cypress Creek gem offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home! Sellers are very motivated.
